# ADR Traceability

- RULE: Every material rule in `.cursor/rules` must map to an ADR.
- RULE: High-impact config files should cite their source ADR when the file format supports comments.
- RULE: Do not invent policy directly inside config files.
- RULE: If doctrine and an existing config disagree, ADR wins and the config must be updated.
